QNapi is a software that helps you download and match subtitles to your movie files. It searches multiple subtitle databases to find the best match for your movie. It also supports multiple operating systems like Windows, OSX, and Linux. You can select the format of the subtitles, like SRT, mDVD, TMP, and MPL2. You can also choose from different languages. It also has features like directory scanning, batch subtitles download and subtitles post-processing like changing file encoding and  setting file permissions. It also has a nice command-line interface. 